# Business DNA Engine

See [BUSINESS_DNA_ENGINE.md](../../BUSINESS_DNA_ENGINE.md).

## Rules

1. Tenant isolation mandatory — all tables scoped by `tenant_id`.
2. Learn from approved sources only; all imports visible in Knowledge Approval Center.
3. Owner/admin required for profile changes (`_bde_require_admin()`).
4. Email responses: template priority → knowledge → tone → default.
5. Human review mode default ON; low confidence always escalates.
6. Business logic in Supabase RPCs; API routes are thin clients.
7. Route: `/app/settings/business-dna` (spec `/admin/business-dna`).
8. Platform: `get_platform_business_dna_overview` — aggregates only.
9. i18n: `customerApp.businessDna.*`, `platform.businessDna.*` in en/no/sv/da.

## Tables

`business_dna_profiles` · `bde_settings` · `business_products` · `business_workflows` · `support_knowledge_items` · `business_email_templates` · `business_tone_profiles` · `business_escalation_rules` · `business_knowledge_sources` · `business_template_suggestions` · `business_email_drafts` · `business_dna_audit_logs`
